1
00:00:00,910 --> 00:00:03,010
(Love In Sync)

2
00:00:09,850 --> 00:00:12,320
(Kim Myung Soo)

3
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:18,990
(Kang Min Ah)

4
00:00:38,710 --> 00:00:41,880
(Love In Sync)

5
00:00:43,720 --> 00:00:44,789
(All people, incidents, and backgrounds...)

6
00:00:44,790 --> 00:00:45,919
(in this drama are fictitious and unrelated to reality.)

7
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:47,120
(Also, children and animals were filmed under production guidelines.)

8
00:00:47,490 --> 00:00:48,890
Let's do it. The kiss.

9
00:00:49,390 --> 00:00:51,130
How can you suggest a kiss so easily?

10
00:00:52,630 --> 00:00:53,630
You don't know my profession?

11
00:00:53,830 --> 00:00:54,830
I am an actress.

12
00:00:58,630 --> 00:00:59,970
If you run away this time, you are dead.

13
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:01,870
It is work, just work.

14
00:01:10,310 --> 00:01:13,010
Gosh.

15
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,749
Is it right to cast a supporting actor...

16
00:01:16,750 --> 00:01:18,219
through an audition without consulting it...

17
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:19,550
with the lead actor?

18
00:01:19,990 --> 00:01:22,290
Do I have to consult with you about something like that?

19
00:01:22,620 --> 00:01:23,630
Yes, you do.

20
00:01:24,090 --> 00:01:26,229
If you cast someone who seems to be of a lower calibre,

21
00:01:26,230 --> 00:01:28,160
the lead actor will also appear to be of a lower calibre.

22
00:01:28,530 --> 00:01:29,959
If you cast someone who stands out too much,

23
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,329
our Yi Jin will be overshadowed,

24
00:01:31,330 --> 00:01:33,370
so how can I not worry about that?

25
00:01:33,870 --> 00:01:36,070
Right? And above all,

26
00:01:37,310 --> 00:01:41,110
this is truly not right, is it?

27
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:43,379
Right? Why is the lead actor...

28
00:01:43,380 --> 00:01:44,649
who stepped down due to a power abuse controversy...

29
00:01:44,650 --> 00:01:46,780
auditioning for a supporting role?

30
00:01:46,950 --> 00:01:50,080
If she wants to audition, is there any reason to stop her?

31
00:01:50,250 --> 00:01:51,289
There is no justification.

32
00:01:51,290 --> 00:01:52,690
We should stop her even if we have to create a justification.

33
00:01:53,290 --> 00:01:54,820
Things are going strangely.

34
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,860
Why are you being so sensitive?

35
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:58,730
Thanks to this, the movie is getting promoted, which is good.

36
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:00,359
Without even needing much marketing,

37
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:02,160
our movie is very popular these days.

38
00:02:02,660 --> 00:02:03,770
That is the problem.

39
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,099
If Ji An, who is merely auditioning for a supporting role,

40
00:02:06,100 --> 00:02:08,499
becomes more popular than our Yi Jin,

41
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:10,239
she will be overshadowed. It is her first time...

42
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:11,340
to be the lead actress.

43
00:02:11,610 --> 00:02:12,669
Oh, gosh.

44
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:13,909
Don't do the audition.

45
00:02:13,910 --> 00:02:16,480
It isn't too late, so cancel that audition.

46
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:19,280
I'll pick out a good one from my agency.

47
00:02:20,620 --> 00:02:23,480
Mr. Kim, are you going to keep acting like this?

48
00:02:25,320 --> 00:02:26,590
Acting like what?

49
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:28,959
If you interfere with every little thing and find fault...

50
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,630
throughout the entire film shoot, then I...

51
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:33,900
cannot work with Han Yi Jin.

52
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:35,960
Director, it is a misunderstanding.

53
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:39,069
Our CEO cares about me, so he is acting like this...

54
00:02:39,070 --> 00:02:41,370
in case I am intimidated. This will not happen again.

55
00:02:42,270 --> 00:02:44,670
If you are so displeased, then just cancel the contract.

56
00:02:45,140 --> 00:02:46,339
- What? - It isn't too late...

57
00:02:46,340 --> 00:02:47,340
since filming has not started yet.

58
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,350
No, Director Moon.

59
00:02:51,810 --> 00:02:52,810
What?

60
00:02:53,250 --> 00:02:55,020
Anyway, Mr. Kim, you are quite a character.

61
00:02:56,650 --> 00:02:57,650
Me? What?

62
00:02:58,090 --> 00:02:59,189
Let's talk later.

63
00:02:59,190 --> 00:03:01,059
Director Moon.

64
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:02,060
Please wait.

65
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:04,960
Anyway, that guy is too arrogant because he is doing well.

66
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,960
Hey.

67
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:14,939
If you came along, you should be a supporter, not a hindrance.

68
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:16,240
Why are you silent as a stone?

69
00:03:16,540 --> 00:03:18,539
That's why I told you I wouldn't go along with you from the start.

70
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:20,010
What's the big deal about a supporting role audition?

71
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:22,209
Do you know how much I'm struggling because of you?

72
00:03:22,210 --> 00:03:23,980
Frankly, if you just had star power,

73
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,150
would I be doing this humiliating thing?

74
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:31,550
Look now.

75
00:03:32,450 --> 00:03:33,450
If you search for the movie title on portals,

76
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:36,119
news about Ji An's supporting role audition comes out first...

77
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,530
before news about you who plays a lead role.

78
00:03:38,990 --> 00:03:39,990
Do you think it makes sense?

79
00:03:40,130 --> 00:03:41,660
That's just buzz.

80
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:44,770
Buzz is popularity, and popularity is star power.

81
00:03:45,470 --> 00:03:47,300
Something you can never take from Yu Ji An.

82
00:03:48,670 --> 00:03:53,069
I guarantee you, if Ji An gets a role through auditioning,

83
00:03:53,070 --> 00:03:54,310
and joins this film as a supporting actress,

84
00:03:54,810 --> 00:03:57,350
it's only a matter of time before you, the lead, get overshadowed.

85
00:03:58,380 --> 00:04:02,050
So, if you don't want to lose what you just barely took back,

86
00:04:02,450 --> 00:04:03,520
you need to stay focused.

87
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:16,529
I've made up my mind.

88
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,200
What decision are you talking about?

89
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:22,339
For a life without regrets, I'll put aside temporary embarrassment.

90
00:04:22,340 --> 00:04:24,770
And I'll do my best with what I can do now.

91
00:04:28,010 --> 00:04:30,140
Oh, no, no. Just now,

92
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:32,280
I must have misheard you, right?

93
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:34,480
You heard correctly.

94
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:35,880
The sound of my heart.

95
00:04:35,980 --> 00:04:37,649
Why are you doing kisses by time of day,

96
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:39,290
changing locations and weather?

97
00:04:39,520 --> 00:04:40,819
Well, I have no choice.

98
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:43,259
The audition is coming up soon, and a kiss is definitely...

99
00:04:43,260 --> 00:04:44,729
what causes emotional transference.

100
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:46,729
Since I could not find any other variable to make it possible,

101
00:04:46,730 --> 00:04:48,630
we have to try everything we can.

102
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:55,900
Then I will start.

103
00:04:58,670 --> 00:05:00,110
No matter how much I think about it,

104
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:02,210
this isn't the right thing to do.

105
00:05:02,540 --> 00:05:04,450
There isn't anything else we can do right now.

106
00:05:06,110 --> 00:05:07,280
Still, this is a bit much.

107
00:05:08,150 --> 00:05:09,179
What is it?

108
00:05:09,180 --> 00:05:11,090
Are you perhaps afraid that you will really fall for me?

109
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:12,950
Oh, well...

110
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:17,590
- No, I am not. - Then why?

111
00:05:18,060 --> 00:05:20,600
It is business, just work.

112
00:05:22,860 --> 00:05:24,030
Who got the audition?

113
00:05:35,580 --> 00:05:36,980
(Closed)

114
00:05:58,770 --> 00:05:59,870
(Tok Tok Mental Care)

115
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:22,859
Finally, we succeeded in kissing...

116
00:06:22,860 --> 00:06:24,990
at all hours of the day.

117
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:28,100
But we failed to reverse the situation.

118
00:06:36,740 --> 00:06:38,040
What should I do?

119
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,870
Today is the day of auditioning, but...

120
00:06:40,370 --> 00:06:41,480
If there is no emotional transference...

121
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,980
You know well about my acting.

122
00:06:45,650 --> 00:06:47,110
Why don't you start practising the acting...

123
00:06:51,550 --> 00:06:52,750
Aren't you thirsty?

124
00:06:53,150 --> 00:06:54,160
Do you want some sparkling water?

125
00:06:54,690 --> 00:06:55,690
I will take it right away.

126
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,540
Please stop it.

127
00:07:11,470 --> 00:07:13,310
Why are you doing this now?

128
00:07:15,210 --> 00:07:16,410
Just leave me alone.

129
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,120
Ji An, are you okay?

130
00:07:27,050 --> 00:07:28,820
(Mom)

131
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,560
Ji An...

132
00:07:31,990 --> 00:07:35,830
actually attempted it before.

133
00:07:36,230 --> 00:07:38,830
There are rumours that it was due to family matters.

134
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,400
There are also rumours that it was because of money.

135
00:07:57,050 --> 00:08:01,060
The first time I lived with my mother...

136
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,220
was when I was seven years old.

137
00:08:05,090 --> 00:08:07,090
Before that, I lived in relatives' houses...

138
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,100
and my maternal grandmother's house.

139
00:08:10,670 --> 00:08:12,530
Then eventually,

140
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:15,370
she sent me to the orphanage.

141
00:08:17,300 --> 00:08:19,670
Do you know where my mother first took me...

142
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,880
after taking me out of the orphanage?

143
00:08:25,810 --> 00:08:27,379
An audition for child models.

144
00:08:27,380 --> 00:08:28,750
Thank you.

145
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:31,220
It is funny, right?

146
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:32,620
Someone said that.

147
00:08:34,059 --> 00:08:36,260
That child models earn a lot of money.

148
00:08:37,860 --> 00:08:40,559
I was pretty even when I was young.

149
00:08:41,530 --> 00:08:43,960
You know, a born natural beauty, right?

150
00:08:48,770 --> 00:08:49,940
I should have been a little less pretty.

151
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:55,640
Then such a tragedy would not have happened in my life.

152
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:00,820
Do you know what the biggest tragedy for my mother and me is?

153
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:04,920
My mother always needs me.

154
00:09:05,620 --> 00:09:08,720
You cannot live as a member of "I Want" forever.

155
00:09:09,620 --> 00:09:12,190
Now is the time to become star Yu Ji An.

156
00:09:13,030 --> 00:09:15,099
Not in a cheap place like this,

157
00:09:15,100 --> 00:09:18,270
we can live in the most luxurious penthouse.

158
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:20,100
As befits us.

159
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,250
I foolishly loved...

160
00:09:41,060 --> 00:09:42,990
that kind of mother.

161
00:09:47,090 --> 00:09:48,100
Just...

162
00:09:50,500 --> 00:09:53,130
I just wanted to be loved by my mother.

163
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,100
("Idol Group 'I Want' Is Disbanded By Yu Ji An's Leaving")

164
00:09:58,070 --> 00:09:59,270
But one day, I realised.

165
00:10:02,010 --> 00:10:03,010
Is it true?

166
00:10:05,410 --> 00:10:07,720
This isn't the time to be getting my makeup done leisurely.

167
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:10,680
I had become someone no one loved.

168
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,630
So I ran away with all my might.

169
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:24,200
I came all this way, fighting for my life.

170
00:10:26,830 --> 00:10:31,870
But you still love your mother so much.

171
00:10:35,680 --> 00:10:36,680
So I am afraid...

172
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:40,850
that she will appear before me again...

173
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:42,920
and ruin me.

174
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:46,120
I am afraid that I will go back to those old days.

175
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:49,420
If it happens,

176
00:10:51,190 --> 00:10:52,660
I will protect you.

177
00:10:56,430 --> 00:10:57,530
I am your manager.

178
00:11:02,270 --> 00:11:03,340
I am sorry.

179
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,440
Mister.

180
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,640
I always thought about it after that day.

181
00:11:09,210 --> 00:11:11,150
If only I hadn't let go of my sister's hand...

182
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:13,450
I am the one who made the biggest mistake.

183
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,779
Why am I the only one...

184
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:17,320
who is perfectly fine?

185
00:11:18,090 --> 00:11:19,290
You must have had a very hard time.

186
00:11:23,420 --> 00:11:24,430
I finally found it.

187
00:11:47,850 --> 00:11:50,820
So, you finally snagged a judge's seat?

188
00:11:51,320 --> 00:11:52,890
Why are you doing this?

189
00:11:53,490 --> 00:11:55,620
I am also a legitimate investor in this film.

190
00:11:56,020 --> 00:11:58,290
I have every right to be in this position.

191
00:11:59,730 --> 00:12:00,730
Isn't that right, Director Moon?

192
00:12:05,630 --> 00:12:08,200
Next, number 358, Yu Ji An, please come in.

193
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:23,619
Hello.

194
00:12:23,620 --> 00:12:24,620
I am Yu Ji An.

195
00:12:24,950 --> 00:12:25,950
It has been a long time.

196
00:12:26,290 --> 00:12:27,290
You have a performance prepared, right?

197
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,320
Yes.

198
00:12:41,470 --> 00:12:42,739
(What are you talking about?)

199
00:12:42,740 --> 00:12:44,000
(The data is gone? Are you serious right now?)

200
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:51,910
What? What are you talking about?

201
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:53,880
The data is gone?

202
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,480
Are you serious right now?

203
00:12:56,450 --> 00:12:58,150
Are you saying she betrayed us?

204
00:12:59,020 --> 00:13:00,720
Gosh, this is driving me crazy.

205
00:13:01,160 --> 00:13:02,560
You don't know what kind of situation we are in right now?

206
00:13:03,460 --> 00:13:04,560
We are almost there.

207
00:13:05,530 --> 00:13:08,300
I am finally able to expose all of her schemes.

208
00:13:10,130 --> 00:13:11,330
But now, betrayal?

209
00:13:11,930 --> 00:13:14,740
Then we are just creating a way for her to escape.

210
00:13:15,340 --> 00:13:17,200
But you are so calm saying that now?

211
00:13:18,170 --> 00:13:19,370
Go find that woman right now.

212
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:20,540
Somehow, right now.

213
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:24,710
("Yu Ji An Passes On The Audition, Assuring Her Comeback")

214
00:13:25,950 --> 00:13:26,950
If Ji An gets a role through auditioning,

215
00:13:26,951 --> 00:13:28,220
and joins this film as a supporting actress,

216
00:13:28,850 --> 00:13:31,420
it's only a matter of time before you, the lead, get overshadowed.

217
00:13:47,230 --> 00:13:48,370
Was I that cute?

218
00:13:49,140 --> 00:13:50,640
No, I was not thinking like that.

219
00:13:50,900 --> 00:13:52,970
It is an error of emotional transference. An error.

220
00:13:55,910 --> 00:13:57,410
I told you it was not. It was an error.

221
00:13:57,850 --> 00:13:59,349
Oh, where is the error?

222
00:13:59,350 --> 00:14:00,550
That is perfectly accurate.

223
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,119
Do not misunderstand. There could be such a thing...

224
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:04,280
as an empathy error. Gosh.

225
00:14:04,790 --> 00:14:06,290
Should we take a picture?

226
00:14:06,590 --> 00:14:07,590
That's great.

227
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:10,120
Dong Gyeong, please take a picture of us.

228
00:14:11,430 --> 00:14:12,430
Me?

229
00:14:15,530 --> 00:14:17,599
(Congratulations on Yu Ji An's Comeback!)

230
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:18,600
Okay.

231
00:14:19,670 --> 00:14:20,670
Okay, I will take it.

232
00:14:21,100 --> 00:14:23,600
One, two, three.

233
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:30,080
I told you it was an error.

234
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:31,950
- I don't think so. - Okay.

235
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,790
Then go on in.

236
00:14:53,170 --> 00:14:54,270
What was that?

237
00:14:54,500 --> 00:14:56,640
I am not someone who got caught cheating.

238
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:08,950
There was a call from the real estate agent.

239
00:15:09,520 --> 00:15:11,520
The people who saw the house today want to sign a contract.

240
00:15:12,090 --> 00:15:13,720
I want to sign a contract tomorrow, right away.

241
00:15:14,220 --> 00:15:15,420
- Song Hwan. - You may not know this,

242
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:18,430
but for someone like me, this kind of house is inconvenient.

243
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:21,260
Then I will call the real estate agent tomorrow.

244
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:24,630
When spring comes,

245
00:15:27,230 --> 00:15:28,370
let's move then.

246
00:15:31,340 --> 00:15:33,210
When winter passes and spring comes...

247
00:15:35,910 --> 00:15:37,080
If we leave the house in spring,

248
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:42,820
I think I will feel less cold.

249
00:15:57,430 --> 00:16:00,099
Gosh, so this was meant to be.

250
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,370
It took a long time to get here.

251
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,300
I look forward to working with you.

252
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,640
I look forward to working with you too.

253
00:16:07,340 --> 00:16:09,109
But how did your acting skills...

254
00:16:09,110 --> 00:16:10,840
improve so much in such a short time?

255
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:12,380
There is a secret to everything.

256
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:19,790
Then I can look forward to it.

257
00:16:21,050 --> 00:16:22,060
Of course.

258
00:16:32,930 --> 00:16:34,800
Ha Yul, are you okay?

259
00:16:35,140 --> 00:16:36,340
Gosh.

260
00:16:45,210 --> 00:16:46,309
It hurts.

261
00:16:46,310 --> 00:16:49,480
- Ha Yul. - It hurts.

262
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:19,349
Stop it. Please stop crying!

263
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:37,970
What happened, Song Hwan?

264
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:40,300
He...

265
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:43,170
abandoned me.

266
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:47,440
The sound of a child crying...

267
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:49,540
He said he was sick and tired of her crying.

268
00:17:51,550 --> 00:17:52,550
But Eun Hwan,

269
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,780
I am also so sick and tired of this.

270
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:03,160
I am so scared of myself.

271
00:18:03,760 --> 00:18:04,760
What should I do?

272
00:18:05,330 --> 00:18:06,330
What should I do about Ha Yul?

273
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:10,830
Please, please help me.

274
00:18:14,570 --> 00:18:16,139
What should I do about Ha Yul?

275
00:18:16,140 --> 00:18:18,040
It's okay. It's okay, Song Hwan.

276
00:18:18,740 --> 00:18:20,110
I am here for you, right?

277
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:32,550
Don't worry too much.

278
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,890
Kids just get hurt as they grow up, you know.

279
00:18:39,930 --> 00:18:40,930
Is Ha Yul okay?

280
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:42,960
Yes, she is okay.

281
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,600
You don't have to worry.

282
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:46,400
- Is she okay? - Don't...

283
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,440
Don't touch my child.

284
00:18:53,740 --> 00:18:54,980
I was just worried.

285
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,310
Who are you to say that?

286
00:18:57,210 --> 00:18:58,510
By what right?

287
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:01,350
If it hadn't been for you...

288
00:19:01,351 --> 00:19:03,920
If it hadn't been for someone like you, my father and I...

289
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,220
Song Hwan.

290
00:19:09,060 --> 00:19:10,720
Please.

291
00:19:24,910 --> 00:19:26,010
I am sorry.

292
00:19:26,710 --> 00:19:27,710
Please pass me Ha Yul.

293
00:19:30,080 --> 00:19:31,680
- Please take care of Ji An. - Okay.

294
00:19:35,850 --> 00:19:37,950
Song Hwan is a bit prickly.

295
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:43,360
We will leave this house as soon as Ha Yul wakes up.

296
00:19:43,660 --> 00:19:44,689
Song Hwan.

297
00:19:44,690 --> 00:19:46,590
I don't want to be treated like baggage by you anymore.

298
00:19:47,490 --> 00:19:48,500
You have done enough, I suppose.

299
00:19:52,130 --> 00:19:54,970
Now, you don't have to be held back by me. Live comfortably.

300
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:59,010
You are not disabled, not like me.

301
00:20:01,810 --> 00:20:05,750
You hate Ji An, don't you?

302
00:20:09,320 --> 00:20:11,280
Yes, I hate her.

303
00:20:11,950 --> 00:20:13,250
I hate her so much.

304
00:20:14,450 --> 00:20:16,120
Every time I struggle with misfortune,

305
00:20:16,690 --> 00:20:18,760
I'm angry because I feel like it's all her fault.

306
00:20:19,590 --> 00:20:20,759
Every time she smiles in front of me,

307
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:22,000
pretending she doesn't know anything,

308
00:20:22,400 --> 00:20:23,900
I want to spit on her.

309
00:20:24,970 --> 00:20:26,329
Are you done?

310
00:20:26,330 --> 00:20:27,330
But Song Hwan,

311
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:30,340
I feel sorry for that woman.

312
00:20:32,910 --> 00:20:35,280
Living with guilt on her back...

313
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:38,650
It seems like she's similar to me.

314
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:44,249
I know how suffocating it is to live...

315
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:48,890
while enduring the gaze of someone who resents me.

316
00:20:53,030 --> 00:20:54,130
I know it best.

317
00:20:56,160 --> 00:20:58,059
- Cha Eun Hwan. - I know.

318
00:20:58,060 --> 00:20:59,130
Song Hwan, I know everything.

319
00:21:00,070 --> 00:21:01,369
That is why I am hesitating.

320
00:21:01,370 --> 00:21:02,870
I stop and will not go any further.

321
00:21:05,540 --> 00:21:06,540
Just three months.

322
00:21:08,070 --> 00:21:09,380
Just three months in this place.

323
00:21:12,010 --> 00:21:13,010
During that period...

324
00:21:16,380 --> 00:21:17,880
Can you please cut me slack?

325
00:21:26,860 --> 00:21:27,860
Cha Eun Hwan.

326
00:21:29,030 --> 00:21:30,460
- What happened? - I don't want to be...

327
00:21:30,860 --> 00:21:32,030
involved with you anymore.

328
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:36,300
- Is she okay? - Don't touch my child.

329
00:21:36,700 --> 00:21:38,970
Who are you to say that? By what right?

330
00:21:54,390 --> 00:21:55,790
What business do you have with me?

331
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:58,330
I think I need to know now.

332
00:22:00,030 --> 00:22:01,730
The inexplicable hostility you showed me...

333
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:05,230
from the first time we met,

334
00:22:06,130 --> 00:22:07,769
and Eun Hwan's mind...

335
00:22:07,770 --> 00:22:10,270
which made him confused while looking at me.

336
00:22:11,970 --> 00:22:12,970
I want to know the reason of them.

337
00:22:15,110 --> 00:22:16,110
Tell me.

338
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:18,139
What did you mean yesterday when you said...

339
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:19,850
it was because of me?

340
00:22:20,610 --> 00:22:23,050
Do you really want to know?

341
00:22:32,860 --> 00:22:33,860
It meant nothing.

342
00:22:35,630 --> 00:22:36,630
What?

343
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,430
Yesterday, you clearly said it was because of me.

344
00:22:38,570 --> 00:22:40,000
I was just angry and said whatever came to mind.

345
00:22:41,370 --> 00:22:43,270
I am tired, so please leave.

346
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:13,800
- Are you alright? - Please save me.

347
00:23:14,130 --> 00:23:15,870
I will definitely save you.

348
00:23:37,020 --> 00:23:38,020
Aren't you getting ready?

349
00:23:39,290 --> 00:23:40,989
Today is the day for your costume fitting.

350
00:23:40,990 --> 00:23:42,459
- Excuse me... - You will be late.

351
00:23:42,460 --> 00:23:43,760
Please get ready quickly.

352
00:24:00,550 --> 00:24:03,419
If I had not touched Father's respirator,

353
00:24:03,420 --> 00:24:06,520
perhaps all this misfortune would have passed us by.

354
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:08,790
Right.

355
00:24:09,120 --> 00:24:10,320
It cannot be.

356
00:24:10,960 --> 00:24:13,060
I will definitely save you.

357
00:24:14,490 --> 00:24:16,700
I am sorry, mister.

358
00:24:17,730 --> 00:24:18,800
It cannot be.

359
00:24:24,070 --> 00:24:25,110
Yes.

360
00:24:29,340 --> 00:24:30,340
Why? What is it?

361
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:36,520
Well... Thank you for this morning.

362
00:24:37,220 --> 00:24:38,220
I have no other intentions.

363
00:24:38,620 --> 00:24:40,420
It is just that I hate things getting complicated.

364
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:44,320
Anyway, all we have to do is leave, right?

365
00:24:47,330 --> 00:24:48,330
It will be spring, right?

366
00:24:50,260 --> 00:24:51,800
If we pretend not to know until then,

367
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:53,330
then it will be fine, right?

368
00:24:55,640 --> 00:24:56,640
Yes.

369
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,510
Thank you, Song Hwan.

370
00:25:05,350 --> 00:25:06,350
But do you know that?

371
00:25:08,550 --> 00:25:10,580
You are more cruel to Yu Ji An than I am.

372
00:25:12,720 --> 00:25:15,220
You are at least preparing for this,

373
00:25:15,320 --> 00:25:17,289
but from Yu Ji An's perspective, it will feel like she is struck...

374
00:25:17,290 --> 00:25:18,430
by lightning.

375
00:25:20,130 --> 00:25:22,460
She'll feel that miserable feeling,

376
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:24,830
being abandoned by someone for no reason.

377
00:25:33,270 --> 00:25:34,310
How could...

378
00:25:34,440 --> 00:25:35,440
Both of you...

379
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:36,710
Right.

380
00:25:37,880 --> 00:25:38,909
Say hello.

381
00:25:38,910 --> 00:25:41,650
This is Manager Cha, who is now my real manager.

382
00:25:47,790 --> 00:25:48,960
I am also suspicious of that.

383
00:25:49,590 --> 00:25:51,290
Because the alibi times match exactly.

384
00:25:52,360 --> 00:25:53,489
Jung In speaks with an excited face,

385
00:25:53,490 --> 00:25:54,930
which does not suit the situation.

386
00:25:58,260 --> 00:26:00,269
Right. It is like he wants...

387
00:26:00,270 --> 00:26:02,040
to play a game with us.

388
00:26:02,970 --> 00:26:03,970
It's making me excited.

389
00:26:04,740 --> 00:26:07,710
It is like he put us into a game that was already set up.

390
00:26:08,840 --> 00:26:11,640
Have you met that woman, his wife, by any chance?

391
00:26:12,410 --> 00:26:16,179
Next, scene 33. Su Ji hears the news of her husband's death...

392
00:26:16,180 --> 00:26:18,320
and cries out like a wailing beast.

393
00:26:20,090 --> 00:26:23,460
Say hello. This is Manager Cha, who is now my real manager.

394
00:26:23,860 --> 00:26:27,159
So, if you don't want to lose what you just barely took back,

395
00:26:27,160 --> 00:26:28,430
you need to stay focused.

396
00:26:33,730 --> 00:26:34,730
No.

397
00:26:35,100 --> 00:26:36,100
That cannot be.

398
00:26:37,340 --> 00:26:38,370
Why my husband?

399
00:26:38,610 --> 00:26:40,110
Who did this?

400
00:26:46,150 --> 00:26:47,480
Detective, please.

401
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:51,220
Please save my husband.

402
00:26:52,190 --> 00:26:53,490
What should I do?

403
00:26:55,090 --> 00:26:57,320
How should I live now?

404
00:27:11,770 --> 00:27:13,340
I am not intimidated by Yi Jin.

405
00:27:13,840 --> 00:27:15,110
I am worried.

406
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:17,240
Because tomorrow is my first shoot.

407
00:27:17,840 --> 00:27:18,850
Who said anything?

408
00:27:19,210 --> 00:27:20,750
You just said something.

409
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:22,180
I heard everything.

410
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:25,749
You always reveal other people's true feelings...

411
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:27,020
without permission.

412
00:27:29,790 --> 00:27:30,890
Shall we go to Han River?

413
00:27:33,430 --> 00:27:35,629
Once filming starts, I will not be able to move.

414
00:27:35,630 --> 00:27:37,130
So, we can heal ourselves before then.

415
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:41,200
You are an actress, and you're not managing your condition?

416
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,770
What if you catch a cold?

417
00:27:42,900 --> 00:27:44,100
It will affect the shoot.

418
00:27:44,340 --> 00:27:45,939
No, who said I would be there for a long time?

419
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:47,410
Let's get some fresh air for a moment.

420
00:27:47,740 --> 00:27:50,280
What if you get caught up in a baseless rumour like last time?

421
00:27:51,140 --> 00:27:53,179
If you get into a scandal with a manager...

422
00:27:53,180 --> 00:27:55,180
who you have no relationship with,

423
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,220
it won't be good for your image.

424
00:27:58,820 --> 00:28:00,049
Alright. I am not going.

425
00:28:00,050 --> 00:28:01,250
Is that enough?

426
00:28:07,990 --> 00:28:11,530
What kind of relationship do you have with Yi Jin?

427
00:28:12,500 --> 00:28:13,700
Is she someone special to you?

428
00:28:14,630 --> 00:28:17,469
Yi Jin and I are simply a client...

429
00:28:17,470 --> 00:28:19,310
and a counsellor.

430
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:22,440
Right?

431
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:23,980
I thought so.

432
00:28:24,710 --> 00:28:27,810
It's just that she was my first client, so it's a bit more special.

433
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:31,180
Special, my foot.

434
00:28:35,090 --> 00:28:36,820
What did you consult her about?

435
00:28:38,360 --> 00:28:40,090
She didn't seem to be struggling at all.

436
00:28:44,800 --> 00:28:45,829
What is this?

437
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:47,300
This feeling of being curious about me?

438
00:28:47,930 --> 00:28:48,940
I am just proud of you.

439
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:51,199
I am so proud of you...

440
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,910
because you're finally curious about such things.

441
00:28:55,440 --> 00:28:56,440
However...

442
00:28:57,410 --> 00:28:59,449
The content of counselling must not be disclosed to others.

443
00:28:59,450 --> 00:29:00,450
That is a counselling principle.

444
00:29:01,650 --> 00:29:04,050
If you are really curious, think about it.

445
00:29:05,120 --> 00:29:07,320
Why a young female celebrity named Han Yi Jin...

446
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:11,320
came to a counsellor after her group disbanded.

447
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:13,430
Thinking about such things...

448
00:29:13,930 --> 00:29:15,060
That would be empathy.

449
00:29:39,990 --> 00:29:41,590
Ji An, how about this outfit for today?

450
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:43,689
It's good.

451
00:29:43,690 --> 00:29:44,760
Should I wear this one next?

452
00:29:45,020 --> 00:29:46,030
Oh, yes, that will be nice.

453
00:29:46,930 --> 00:29:47,930
You know how to cinch the waist here, right?

454
00:29:48,190 --> 00:29:49,229
- Oh, I know, I know. - Like this. Okay.

455
00:29:49,230 --> 00:29:50,429
I know you are pretty, but today you are especially pretty.

456
00:29:50,430 --> 00:29:52,229
- Hello. Yu Ji An from I Want. - Hello.

457
00:29:52,230 --> 00:29:53,770
Would an interview be possible for a moment?

458
00:29:54,070 --> 00:29:55,539
Thank you. Let's move slightly.

459
00:29:55,540 --> 00:29:57,070
We will move slightly.

460
00:29:58,040 --> 00:30:01,110
You've returned with I Want's album with all members this time.

461
00:30:01,410 --> 00:30:03,210
Please say a word to your waiting fans.

462
00:30:05,650 --> 00:30:07,180
Yes, until now, I Want...

463
00:30:07,450 --> 00:30:08,450
Just a moment.

464
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:10,620
Ji An, could you please do it?

465
00:30:13,990 --> 00:30:16,119
Yes, to all the fans who have waited for us until now,

466
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:17,490
thank you very much.

467
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:20,229
We prepared this album very diligently,

468
00:30:20,230 --> 00:30:22,700
so please give us a lot of attention and endless love.

469
00:30:23,030 --> 00:30:25,900
Then, so far, I Want!

470
00:30:26,370 --> 00:30:28,069
- Yes, I Want... Yes, thank you. - Thank you.

471
00:30:28,070 --> 00:30:29,670
Please look forward to I Want's full-group album.

472
00:30:29,770 --> 00:30:30,770
Thank you.

473
00:30:32,770 --> 00:30:35,740
("'I Want' Is Disbanded And Yu Ji An Will Debut As A Solo")

474
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,250
Please walk slowly.

475
00:30:45,520 --> 00:30:46,520
You are walking this fast because it's the first shoot?

476
00:30:46,990 --> 00:30:47,990
Just come with me.

477
00:30:51,320 --> 00:30:53,430
Why are you doing this? You are embarrassing me.

478
00:30:54,430 --> 00:30:55,430
Am I a grade schooler?

479
00:30:56,130 --> 00:30:57,859
You're not an overprotective parent.

480
00:30:57,860 --> 00:30:59,200
What? You're embarrassed?

481
00:30:59,570 --> 00:31:01,600
Hey, why are we doing this for?

482
00:31:03,770 --> 00:31:04,770
Is it because of me?

483
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:06,340
Of course.

484
00:31:07,570 --> 00:31:10,080
As a rule, no one dislikes it when you feed them.

485
00:31:10,580 --> 00:31:13,480
The one who feeds gets more respect than the one who does not.

486
00:31:13,710 --> 00:31:14,710
That is how life is.

487
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:16,620
Who knows.

488
00:31:17,420 --> 00:31:19,690
They might even give you an extra reflector over Ji An.

489
00:31:20,190 --> 00:31:21,750
That Ji An is truly something.

490
00:31:22,820 --> 00:31:24,019
Just stay still.

491
00:31:24,020 --> 00:31:25,060
We will take care of everything.

492
00:31:25,490 --> 00:31:26,890
Ji An was also raised this way.

493
00:31:35,600 --> 00:31:37,300
Speak of the devil, and she shall appear.

494
00:31:38,470 --> 00:31:39,570
That is a very good thing.

495
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:42,310
I like that it isn't obvious.

496
00:31:45,650 --> 00:31:47,880
How is it, being a manager?

497
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:50,050
It isn't easy, is it?

498
00:31:51,450 --> 00:31:52,850
Not really.

499
00:31:54,350 --> 00:31:56,760
I know everything without you saying it.

500
00:31:57,960 --> 00:32:00,660
Ji An's temper isn't ordinary.

501
00:32:01,190 --> 00:32:03,430
Her capriciousness is also deadly.

502
00:32:03,860 --> 00:32:05,969
Even now, if she isn't in a good mood,

503
00:32:05,970 --> 00:32:07,370
she acts up, doesn't she?

504
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:11,000
- Not really. - What?

505
00:32:14,910 --> 00:32:16,510
Why have you been speaking informally to me since earlier?

506
00:32:18,410 --> 00:32:19,410
Because you spoke informally to me first?

507
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:23,580
You seem to care a lot about your actors.

508
00:32:24,050 --> 00:32:26,120
The CEO even comes to the set in person.

509
00:32:27,320 --> 00:32:28,720
Even though I am a CEO of the company,

510
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:31,890
I care for them with the heart of their fathers'.

511
00:32:33,530 --> 00:32:34,530
As for me,

512
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:39,800
I truly think of my actors as my own children.

513
00:32:41,930 --> 00:32:42,970
Indeed.

514
00:32:45,000 --> 00:32:46,840
But it seems Ji An was disowned.

515
00:32:49,610 --> 00:32:51,839
No, during the power abuse controversy,

516
00:32:51,840 --> 00:32:53,410
it seemed like you didn't protect her like parents.

517
00:32:54,350 --> 00:32:56,420
There was no attempt to settle with the victim, no media control,

518
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,450
and no legal action at all.

519
00:33:00,850 --> 00:33:01,850
Oh, that was...

520
00:33:02,120 --> 00:33:04,020
The timing was so bad at that time.

521
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:06,029
She wasn't even our agency's actress anymore,

522
00:33:06,030 --> 00:33:07,330
so what right did I have?

523
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:09,000
Frankly, what obligation did I have?

524
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:11,660
Indeed. I also find that very strange.

525
00:33:13,430 --> 00:33:16,699
How such a controversy erupted at a perfect time...

526
00:33:16,700 --> 00:33:18,340
for Ji An to take all the blame alone.

527
00:33:19,410 --> 00:33:23,680
As if someone did it on purpose.

528
00:33:28,410 --> 00:33:30,480
Alright, let's take a picture before the first shoot.

529
00:33:30,750 --> 00:33:31,820
Everyone, please gather around.

530
00:33:32,450 --> 00:33:33,590
Yes, please gather here.

531
00:33:34,190 --> 00:33:35,190
Yes.

532
00:33:37,990 --> 00:33:39,530
Yes, please gather here.

533
00:33:47,570 --> 00:33:50,700
Well... That spot is for the lead actor.

534
00:33:54,010 --> 00:33:55,110
Right.

535
00:33:58,480 --> 00:33:59,880
It has become a habit.

536
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:09,120
Alright, we are shooting.

537
00:34:09,820 --> 00:34:11,290
One, two, three.

538
00:34:21,199 --> 00:34:22,969
Ready. Action.

539
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:27,440
What? What did you just say?

540
00:34:29,409 --> 00:34:30,540
What is he doing?

541
00:34:31,179 --> 00:34:33,510
He should be watching Ji An's acting, not the script.

542
00:34:34,179 --> 00:34:35,480
He doesn't have basics down.

543
00:34:36,520 --> 00:34:38,120
What do you want me to do?

544
00:34:40,449 --> 00:34:42,820
I am not an actor who moves according to the script they wrote.

545
00:34:44,020 --> 00:34:46,360
CCTV footage that appears to be Kang Jun Ho has been found.

546
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:49,300
We both fell for their scheme.

547
00:34:51,860 --> 00:34:52,929
Hang up for now.

548
00:34:53,699 --> 00:34:58,240
Who interfered and how?

549
00:35:00,510 --> 00:35:03,040
It means there is someone in this team helping them.

550
00:35:05,240 --> 00:35:06,450
Cut.

551
00:35:08,810 --> 00:35:09,880
Ji An's emotions are so good.

552
00:35:10,220 --> 00:35:11,580
Oh, really?

553
00:35:11,850 --> 00:35:13,490
Yes. Is this your first shoot, right?

554
00:35:13,590 --> 00:35:14,590
Your immersion is incredible.

555
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:18,760
- Still, let's try one more take. - Okay.

556
00:35:24,100 --> 00:35:25,930
You saw people were surprised when I was acting earlier, right?

557
00:35:26,330 --> 00:35:28,800
I am telling you I saw it more than ten times.

558
00:35:29,540 --> 00:35:30,700
I even heard Director Moon's praise.

559
00:35:31,300 --> 00:35:33,710
I am also telling you I heard it more than ten times.

560
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:37,910
Thank you.

561
00:35:39,280 --> 00:35:41,110
This is all thanks to Eun Hwan,

562
00:35:41,810 --> 00:35:44,380
no, Manager Cha.

563
00:35:48,490 --> 00:35:49,720
Should we just sign a lifetime contract?

564
00:35:50,320 --> 00:35:51,789
This time, I will sign a contract with you...

565
00:35:51,790 --> 00:35:53,490
with the best treatment in the industry.

566
00:35:56,130 --> 00:35:58,800
How long are you going to rely on my emotions?

567
00:36:00,930 --> 00:36:01,930
Ji An, you are an actress.

568
00:36:02,670 --> 00:36:04,839
Then you should try to feel your emotions yourself...

569
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:05,940
and act.

570
00:36:08,610 --> 00:36:10,110
Who says I won't?

571
00:36:11,240 --> 00:36:15,149
I am just grateful, anyway.

572
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,650
Three months.

573
00:36:17,680 --> 00:36:19,719
When that contract period ends,

574
00:36:19,720 --> 00:36:21,750
we will go back to our respective places.

575
00:36:23,990 --> 00:36:25,090
Don't forget that.

576
00:36:37,370 --> 00:36:38,800
Sometimes, I lose my temper, but I don't hold grudges.

577
00:36:40,040 --> 00:36:41,170
Why am I suddenly angry now?

578
00:36:41,770 --> 00:36:42,940
No, I cannot understand.

579
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:45,780
Ji Woong has a lot of schedules.

580
00:36:45,950 --> 00:36:48,080
Our Ji An also has just as many schedules.

581
00:36:48,480 --> 00:36:49,779
- No. - It isn't polite...

582
00:36:49,780 --> 00:36:52,280
to give one person the first and last scenes.

583
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:54,620
It was not my anger.

584
00:36:56,720 --> 00:36:57,819
If he's going to act like that behind my back,

585
00:36:57,820 --> 00:36:58,820
why did he act like that in front of me?

586
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:04,560
Look over there.

587
00:37:05,460 --> 00:37:07,270
I saw it. Why?

588
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:11,040
That man is my manager.

589
00:37:12,200 --> 00:37:14,839
Are you bragging about your current manager...

590
00:37:14,840 --> 00:37:16,510
