591
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:18,840
Is this EXchange or something?

592
00:37:20,350 --> 00:37:22,010
I won't send you text messages from now on.

593
00:37:23,920 --> 00:37:25,350
I am sorry. Just a moment.

594
00:37:27,820 --> 00:37:28,820
Yes, I am Yu Ji An's manager.

595
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:32,660
Yes. A commercial?

596
00:37:34,530 --> 00:37:35,530
Oh, yes.

597
00:37:40,100 --> 00:37:41,869
Gosh. How long has it been...

598
00:37:41,870 --> 00:37:43,670
