599
00:37:44,570 --> 00:37:45,600
Is it that good?

600
00:37:45,740 --> 00:37:47,640
You seem happier than when you were cast in a movie.

601
00:37:48,170 --> 00:37:50,580
This commercial is a measure of popularity.

602
00:37:50,980 --> 00:37:54,010
Among them, only the top of the top can film a shampoo commercial.

603
00:37:55,110 --> 00:37:57,880
And most importantly, the unit price is high.

604
00:37:59,050 --> 00:38:00,090
What?

605
00:38:01,220 --> 00:38:04,390
I need to earn money quickly to lift the provisional attachment.

606
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:13,030
At one time, all the posters hanging here had my face on them.

607
00:38:17,640 --> 00:38:20,369
Oh, I heard we were doing a test shoot today,

608
00:38:20,370 --> 00:38:22,940
I practised some poses for the first time in a while, so take a look.

609
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:24,510
Okay.

610
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,159
You are fluttered, right?

611
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:41,490
No, what nonsense.

612
00:38:42,260 --> 00:38:44,359
– Is it really not true? – I said it isn't.

613
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,360
Is that so?

614
00:38:55,540 --> 00:38:56,810
Your heart is beating so fast.

615
00:38:59,850 --> 00:39:00,910
You fool.

616
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:03,020
Do you think you can hide it?

617
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:05,180
What kind of relationship do you think we have?

618
00:39:08,290 --> 00:39:10,060
A relationship where feelings are conveyed.

619
00:39:12,460 --> 00:39:14,290
No matter how mean you are to me,

620
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:17,160
I wouldn't fall for it.

621
00:39:18,660 --> 00:39:20,400
I know it isn't sincere.

622
00:39:25,910 --> 00:39:27,210
So,

623
00:39:28,370 --> 00:39:33,280
