628
00:39:53,200 --> 00:39:55,300
I need to go to the restroom before the meeting.

629
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:57,070
Wait a moment.

630
00:40:11,280 --> 00:40:12,450
Yes, hello.

631
00:40:14,090 --> 00:40:18,320
We are near there. Right in front... What?

632
00:40:18,690 --> 00:40:20,430
You want to cancel the contract now?

633
00:40:21,030 --> 00:40:23,099
We don't want to do this either, but...

634
00:40:23,100 --> 00:40:25,160
Have you not seen the article yet?

635
00:40:29,370 --> 00:40:30,399
("Brand Loves Her, But Consumers Still Refuse Her")

636
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:31,400
("Yu Ji An's New Controversy About Her Commercial")

637
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:34,110
I'm Han Seo Jun, a reporter from the Taejin Sports entertainment desk.

638
00:40:34,710 --> 00:40:35,940
If you have time, let's do a quick interview.

639
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:45,780
Do you want to go to Han River?

640
00:40:50,990 --> 00:40:52,689
So this is...

641
00:40:52,690 --> 00:40:54,390
It is the Han River for comfort.

642
00:40:58,460 --> 00:40:59,670
It is alright.

643
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:01,430
You don't have to worry that much.

644
00:41:03,040 --> 00:41:04,400
It isn't like this is the 1st or 2nd time this has happened.

645
00:41:06,170 --> 00:41:09,580
At this point, even wounds...

646
00:41:12,950 --> 00:41:14,680
I don't get used to them.

647
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:18,250
It still hurts.

648
00:41:21,250 --> 00:41:23,260
Because the truth has not been revealed yet.

649
00:41:24,060 --> 00:41:25,789
When the truth is revealed, then...

650
00:41:25,790 --> 00:41:27,490
What is the...

651
00:41:29,560 --> 00:41:30,730
truth?

652
00:41:33,570 --> 00:41:35,100
Eun Hwan, do you really believe...

653
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:37,640
I didn't do that?

654
00:41:46,310 --> 00:41:47,980
The Yu Ji An I know...

655
00:41:48,380 --> 00:41:49,620
would never do such a thing.

656
00:41:52,750 --> 00:41:53,920
Gosh.

657
00:41:55,450 --> 00:41:56,560
You're serious.

658
00:42:00,130 --> 00:42:01,430
That's touching.

659
00:42:03,100 --> 00:42:04,600
But what should I do?

660
00:42:05,730 --> 00:42:07,030
I did it.

661
00:42:09,170 --> 00:42:11,840
I was so embarrassed that I didn't want to say this.

662
00:42:13,470 --> 00:42:15,070
That video...

663
00:42:16,110 --> 00:42:17,110
They said it wasn't manipulated.

664
00:42:20,110 --> 00:42:21,410
They said it was the original.

665
00:42:23,150 --> 00:42:24,150
So,

666
00:42:25,420 --> 00:42:27,120
they say I really did that...

667
00:42:28,020 --> 00:42:29,320
to Mi Jeong.

668
00:42:34,030 --> 00:42:35,030
What should I do?

669
00:42:36,830 --> 00:42:38,030
I feel sorry for Mi Jeong.

670
00:42:48,610 --> 00:42:49,910
You have no idea what kind of situation this is...

671
00:42:51,280 --> 00:42:52,280
What is it now?

672
00:42:52,850 --> 00:42:54,950
Are you brutally executing someone who turned themselves in?

673
00:42:56,180 --> 00:42:57,180
Just look at it first.

674
00:42:58,380 --> 00:42:59,490
You have no idea, right?

675
00:43:01,120 --> 00:43:03,120
Oh, this is so frustrating. It is so annoying.

676
00:43:03,620 --> 00:43:05,520
What are all these problems after recruiting a wrong person?

677
00:43:06,630 --> 00:43:07,630
Isn't something a little strange?

678
00:43:08,560 --> 00:43:09,560
What is it?

679
00:43:10,130 --> 00:43:11,999
You know that your language proficiency...

680
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,730
