681
00:43:14,830 --> 00:43:16,869
Me? Not at all.

682
00:43:16,870 --> 00:43:17,970
I have never heard that before.

683
00:43:19,910 --> 00:43:21,010
Is that so?

684
00:43:21,140 --> 00:43:22,810
Since you heard it now, keep it in mind from now on.

685
00:43:24,440 --> 00:43:25,639
Someone like Ji An,

686
00:43:25,640 --> 00:43:29,180
who lacks language proficiency and are immature in emotional control,

687
00:43:30,120 --> 00:43:33,290
