688
00:43:34,390 --> 00:43:36,760
She is speaking so precisely and smoothly, isn't she?

689
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:39,020
Why are you crying?

690
00:43:39,460 --> 00:43:41,659
- Because of you... - It's like she is reciting lines...

691
00:43:41,660 --> 00:43:43,260
from a drama she memorized.

692
00:43:43,700 --> 00:43:46,400
I told you not to cry.

693
00:43:47,470 --> 00:43:48,999
Did you practice lines with Mi Jeong...

694
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,500
