695
00:43:52,140 --> 00:43:53,470
Almost every project.

696
00:43:56,880 --> 00:43:58,410
So, what you're saying is...

697
00:43:59,240 --> 00:44:01,610
I was not actually abusing my power in the video,

698
00:44:02,610 --> 00:44:03,980
but practising lines?

699
00:44:04,780 --> 00:44:06,989
And Mi Jeong maliciously edited it...

700
00:44:06,990 --> 00:44:09,190
and uploaded it as an abuse of power video?

701
00:44:11,420 --> 00:44:12,520
Probably.

702
00:44:13,190 --> 00:44:14,730
No, why?

703
00:44:15,790 --> 00:44:18,700
Why would Mi Jeong do that to me?

704
00:44:19,700 --> 00:44:21,000
I don't know.

705
00:44:21,430 --> 00:44:23,740
We will only know for sure after meeting her.

706
00:44:25,140 --> 00:44:27,110
It could be for her own personal goal.

707
00:44:28,270 --> 00:44:31,510
Or it could be that she was paid by someone...

708
00:44:32,440 --> 00:44:34,310
