709
00:44:38,250 --> 00:44:39,550
Can you even think?

710
00:44:40,120 --> 00:44:42,150
You have no idea what kind of situation this is, do you?

711
00:44:43,660 --> 00:44:46,689
The video isn't manipulated, so the situation cannot be false.

712
00:44:46,690 --> 00:44:48,359
What are all these problems after recruiting a wrong person?

713
00:44:48,360 --> 00:44:50,930
What cases are there where it isn't the truth?

714
00:44:51,160 --> 00:44:52,199
Hey.

715
00:44:52,200 --> 00:44:54,130
I am genuinely curious, so I am asking you.

716
00:44:54,630 --> 00:44:56,170
Does your family know you act like this?

717
00:44:57,740 --> 00:44:59,240
Oh, look at her.

718
00:44:59,970 --> 00:45:00,970
Are you crying?

719
00:45:00,971 --> 00:45:04,080
Hey, why are you crying?

720
00:45:04,480 --> 00:45:06,480
Who should be crying because of you right now?

721
00:45:07,810 --> 00:45:08,850
Don't cry.

722
00:45:09,110 --> 00:45:10,350
I told you not to cry.

723
00:45:13,920 --> 00:45:16,560
(Universe in the Room)

724
00:45:19,890 --> 00:45:21,729
I received the call and checked.

725
00:45:21,730 --> 00:45:23,530
The Universe in the Room was an independent film.

726
00:45:23,860 --> 00:45:25,130
An independent film?

727
00:45:26,200 --> 00:45:28,030
A top star like Ji An?

728
00:45:28,500 --> 00:45:34,340
Back then, she was pretending to be artsy for a long time,

729
00:45:35,040 --> 00:45:37,339
so she made many special appearances in independent films...

730
00:45:37,340 --> 00:45:40,210
to build up her acting skills and to transform her image.

731
00:45:40,450 --> 00:45:42,179
But why can't I find any information about the film...

732
00:45:42,180 --> 00:45:43,180
