733
00:45:43,620 --> 00:45:44,620
There is no way you would find any.

734
00:45:45,180 --> 00:45:46,320
The production was cancelled early on.

735
00:45:46,920 --> 00:45:47,920
So, there is no data.

736
00:45:49,350 --> 00:45:50,360
Is that so?

737
00:45:51,620 --> 00:45:54,290
Then what about the script she received at the time?

738
00:45:54,960 --> 00:45:56,060
That's gone too.

739
00:45:56,860 --> 00:45:58,259
I don't know about anything else,

740
00:45:58,260 --> 00:45:59,970
but one thing I remember clearly is this.

741
00:46:00,270 --> 00:46:02,299
They were worried the script would be leaked,

742
00:46:02,300 --> 00:46:04,870
so they only sent the parts Ji An appeared through quick service.

743
00:46:05,640 --> 00:46:07,510
However...

744
00:46:08,170 --> 00:46:09,680
Why are you so curious about that movie?

745
00:46:12,440 --> 00:46:14,750
- It's nothing. - Okay.

746
00:46:15,980 --> 00:46:17,580
I will be going now.

747
00:46:21,890 --> 00:46:22,890
What are you doing?

748
00:46:23,720 --> 00:46:24,720
Do Hoon.

749
00:46:26,020 --> 00:46:27,930
Isn't the stigma of being a traitor...

750
00:46:28,430 --> 00:46:31,230
- difficult for you? - What?

751
00:46:32,060 --> 00:46:36,700
You are someone who cares about Ji An.

752
00:46:39,710 --> 00:46:41,740
Can you see it, Counsellor?

753
00:46:42,870 --> 00:46:43,880
That mind toward her?

754
00:46:45,140 --> 00:46:46,550
I am a psychological counsellor, you know.

755
00:46:47,510 --> 00:46:50,149
That is why I want to give you...

756
00:46:50,150 --> 00:46:52,350
