778
00:48:08,290 --> 00:48:10,030
Are you telling me to search through all those thousands of people?

779
00:48:10,800 --> 00:48:11,800
Are you crazy?

780
00:48:12,160 --> 00:48:13,170
We have no choice.

781
00:48:13,670 --> 00:48:15,100
This is the best option in this situation.

782
00:48:15,930 --> 00:48:17,339
If we find that director, we can clear...

783
00:48:17,340 --> 00:48:19,570
Ji An's rumour from the power abuse accusation.

784
00:48:20,040 --> 00:48:22,010
Oh, I don't know. Hey, why do I have to do that?

785
00:48:22,340 --> 00:48:23,679
- Because... - I am not doing this...

786
00:48:23,680 --> 00:48:25,280
as a former fan club president.

787
00:48:27,080 --> 00:48:29,150
- Because you are my brother. - What?

788
00:48:29,710 --> 00:48:31,420
Dong Gyeong!

789
00:48:34,250 --> 00:48:35,250
Add the honorific.

790
00:48:37,690 --> 00:48:41,930
My dear Dong Gyeong.

791
00:48:42,630 --> 00:48:47,030
Every time something happens, you always find me.

792
00:48:48,000 --> 00:48:50,470
I will take a look.

793
00:48:53,810 --> 00:48:55,070
Why are you working so hard?

794
00:48:57,740 --> 00:48:58,940
