795
00:48:59,310 --> 00:49:01,250
Are you crazy?

796
00:49:02,250 --> 00:49:03,250
Then what is it?

797
00:49:06,990 --> 00:49:08,120
Just...

798
00:49:15,030 --> 00:49:17,330
I thought breaking up with someone who is smiling...

799
00:49:18,260 --> 00:49:19,430
